snippet.title: STAR WARS™: The Force Unleashed™ | Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to wield the devastating power of The Force and your own lightsaber?

We’re thrilled to announce that we’ll be bringing the Nintendo Wii version of STAR WARS™: The Force Unleashed™ to Nintendo Switch on April 20th, 2022!

Pre-order now 👇
https://aspyr.link/SWTFU-US

-----

For 25 years, we've helped some of the biggest games become game-changers. Learn more about who we are and what we do ► https://aspyr.com/
